        "text": [
            "The &ldquo;Single-window&rdquo; (one-stop-shop) system initiates the process of reviewing proposals in the company on the use of products / work performed / services provided without sending official requests. Any organization or individual can send a cooperation offer &ndash; use of equipment, introduction of new technologies, provision of services, performance of work, etc.",
            "To send a proposal, it is necessary to define a category &ndash; Innovative solutions, Innovative project idea, Products / services provided / work performed (section &ldquo;Cooperation offers&rdquo;), or Open requests (questions not related to the previous groups). Next, it is required to draw up an application according to the proposed form and send it to the Company."
